<lyrics>[V1]
 1- dạymạaⁿ tsmʿ lṣlạty qlbk sẖạʿr ạ̉nạty
 qbl mạ ạ̉jylk wạ̉ḥkylk ạ̉lqạk tsmʿ lậhạty
 wtjạwb ʿly̱ ṣrkẖạty tnqdẖny fy wqt ḍyqạty
 wfy lḥẓẗ lmạ ạ̉nạdylk ạlqạk tsrʿ lnjạty
 2-ʿạlm kl ạ̉ḥtyạjạty rgẖm hmwmy wḥsạbạty
 ạ̉rfʿ qlby wạ̉ṣlylk wạlqạk ʿạrf ṭlbạty
 wbtsẖhd kl ḥyạty qṣẗ ʿmry wḥkạyạty
 ʿn nʿmh wkẖyr wmrạḥm fy mạḍy wʿmry ạlậty
 3-mạ fy ywm ṭwlt ʿly ạ̹lạ qṣdk kẖyr ly
 tẖqty fy ḥbk yạ fạdy mlyạn rḥmh wḥnyh
 dh kfạyh ʿly̱ wjwdk lmạ ạ̉ṣrkẖlk bwʿwdk
 msẖ ʿạyz ḥd swạk yạ mḥly̱ ạlgẖrbh bjwdk</lyrics>
